---
layout: layouts/base.njk
---
<div class="container">
<div class="row mt-5">
<div class="col-md-10 mx-auto p-3 p-md-5">
<h1 class="lead col-md-8"><strong><small><a href="{{page.url}}" title="{{title}}">{{title}}</a></small></strong></h1>
<h2 class="title"><strong>{{intro}}</strong></h2>
<p class="mt-3">{{description}}</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid">
<div class="col-md-11 mx-auto p-3">
<div class="ratio ratio-16x9 mb-3">
<iframe src="{{video}}" title="{{title}}" loading="lazy"></iframe>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-10 mx-auto p-3">
{{ content |safe }}
</div>
<div class="col-md-10 mx-auto p-3">
<div class="border border-primary rounder p-3 p-md-5">
<h3><a href="{{page.title}}" title="{{product.title}}">{{product.title}}</a></h3>
<p>
Untuk mendapatkan informasi mengenai bagaimana spesifikasi dan fitur serta konsep kerja {{product.title}} , Kunjungi halaman informasi detail.
</p>
<p><a href="{{product.link}}">
Informasi lebih lanjut tentang {{product.title}} →
</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
{%- if collections.demoapps %}
{%- set previousPost = collections.demoapps| getPreviousCollectionItem %}
{%- set nextPost = collections.demoapps | getNextCollectionItem %}
{%- if nextPost or previousPost %}
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-6 p-3">
{%- if previousPost %}
<div class="p-3 bg-dark rounder">
<p><small>← Terbaru</small></p>
<h3><a href="{{ previousPost.url }}">{{ previousPost.data.title }}</a></h3>
</div>
{% endif %}
</div>
<div class="col-md-6 p-3 text-end">
{%- if nextPost %}
<div class="p-3 bg-dark rounder">
<p><small>Selanjutnya →</small></p>
<h3><a href="{{ nextPost.url }}">{{ nextPost.data.title }}</a></h3>
</div>
{% endif %}
</div>
</div>
</div>
{%- endif %}
{%- endif %}
</div>